sub_title: Co-founder & Business Development at Forward · Inc
summary:
On a mission with Forward·Inc to support 5000 entrepreneurs with a refugee background to start their business by 2025.   

I love helping entrepreneurs launch their business and helping started entrepreneurs to become daring, innovative and impactful. 

Firm believer in radical change in attitudes of business, NGO and government to foster entrepreneurship and social impact.
